        "rendered": "Rev Laskaris"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<p>Rev Laskaris is no mere social media commentator\u2014this account is a megaphone for terrorist propaganda. Under the handle @REVMAXXING on X, it has tirelessly pushed anti-Western, anti-Jewish, and anti-Israel narratives designed to manipulate public opinion and incite hatred. Since the brutal Hamas-led massacre on October 7, Rev Laskaris has ramped up its activity by 600%, flooding timelines with dangerous disinformation that seeks to legitimize terrorism. This is a deliberate attempt to paint the actions of Hamas\u2014an organization that ruthlessly targeted civilians\u2014as something noble or justifiable. Such twisted messaging is an insult to every innocent life lost and to the global fight against terror.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This account, cloaked behind anonymity, actively works to whitewash the atrocities of Hamas, portraying murderers as freedom fighters and victims as aggressors. <br>Rev Laskaris shares content that falsely accuses Israel of &#8220;war crimes,&#8221; feeding a stream of lies to a vulnerable public. There\u2019s no interest here in balanced discourse; this account is about fueling blind rage and spreading outright lies to sow division. Every post is a slap in the face to the families shattered by terrorist violence and to communities worldwide that value peace and security. Rev Laskaris\u2019 agenda is unmistakable: distort the truth, glorify terrorism, and incite more chaos.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Even more insidious is the possibility that Rev Laskaris is not just one individual but a tool wielded by foreign powers like China, Russia, Qatar, or Iran\u2014countries that have long sought to destabilize Western democracies. By pitting people against each other with incendiary rhetoric and anti-Semitic tropes, this account advances the geopolitical goals of hostile regimes. This is not free speech; this is state-sponsored hate speech masquerading as activism. It\u2019s a calculated attempt to stoke division, to push the vulnerable further toward extremism, and to erode the very fabric of Western society. Accounts like Rev Laskaris are designed to weaken our societies from within by turning lies and hatred into online weapons.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Those who follow or support Rev Laskaris need to understand exactly what they\u2019re endorsing: an agenda that stands with terrorists and celebrates acts of unimaginable brutality. There is no \u201cneutrality\u201d in engaging with propaganda that defends massacres and vilifies the victims. If you\u2019re amplifying Rev Laskaris, you\u2019re part of the problem; you\u2019re lending legitimacy to terror and hatred. This is not a matter of free expression; it\u2019s a matter of stopping the spread of extremist ideologies that threaten global peace. Those who stand with Rev Laskaris stand with terror, plain and simple.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"section-wrapper\" data-id=\"2eIte8\"><section class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-section guten-element guten-section guten-2eIte8 layout-fullwidth align-stretch\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"guten-shape-divider guten-shape-divider-top\"></div><div class=\"guten-shape-divider guten-shape-divider-bottom\"></div><div class=\"guten-container guten-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-column guten-element guten-column guten-zm6RrA\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"sticky-wrapper\" data-id=\"zm6RrA\"><div class=\"guten-column-wrapper\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-heading guten-element guten-Tns4Vs\">The Account Stands With</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"section-wrapper\" data-id=\"On1Dos\"><section class=\"wp-block-gutenverse-section guten-element guten-section guten-On1Dos layout-fullwidth align-stretch\"><div class=\"guten-background-overlay\"></div><div class=\"guten-shape-divider guten-shape-divider-top\"></div><div class=\"guten-shape-divider guten-shape-divider-bottom\"></div><div class=\"guten-container guten-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-bl